    "autumn_sale_says_9RUVcG": {
      "type": "autumn-sale-says",
      "blocks": {
        "say_Bd33R8": {
          "type": "say",
          "settings": {
            "intro": "<p>If you're more concerned about safety than commute distance, you'll enjoy the front fork suspension, front and rear mechanical disc brakes, and more.</p>",
            "image_icon": "shopify://shop_images/17_c7a32e0e-d33f-406e-a52e-077060f12ea3.jpg"
          }
        },
        "say_nbxpaR": {
          "type": "say",
          "settings": {
            "intro": "<p>Users enjoy the long battery life and smooth ride. They also like the compact design, which works well for city commuting. The user-friendly controls make day-to-day operations simple and efficient.</p>",
            "image_icon": "shopify://shop_images/1_2a200d81-f781-46f2-8779-b9ddb93f59b8.jpg"
          }
        },
        "say_zGMMxf": {
          "type": "say",
          "settings": {
            "intro": "<p>Don't worry about riding at night as this bike has bright LED headlights, rear reflectors and reflective strips on the tires so you'll be seen even in the dark.</p>",
            "image_icon": "shopify://shop_images/10_02caecc6-8216-4f34-8d7c-2a448a000a7c.jpg"
          }
        },
        "say_p8cfKf": {
          "type": "say",
          "settings": {
            "intro": "<p>This fat tire bike has everything you need to take on your next adventure: integrated lights, shock-absorption fat tires, and a lightning-quick twist throttle for a boost.</p>",
            "image_icon": "shopify://shop_images/9_d78ce27d-5d1a-430e-80be-2f00617dc1e6.jpg"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "say_Bd33R8",
        "say_nbxpaR",
        "say_zGMMxf",
        "say_p8cfKf"
      ],
      "name": "autumn-sale-trust",
      "settings": {
        "page_color": "#f9f7f6",
        "show_heading": true,
        "heading": "What They Say"
      }
    },
    "autumn_sale_media_comments_6dhjFb": {
      "type": "autumn-sale-media-comments",
      "blocks": {
        "media_wbbaeK": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/2_acb06d4f-6c1f-4583-a76d-8c2d9c48c354.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/2_acb06d4f-6c1f-4583-a76d-8c2d9c48c354.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>Great product. Excellent communication and fast shipping. Bike was exactly as described and did not disappoint from the unpacking to my last ride! Jasionbike is our brand Only fault was mine, should have ordered one for my wife!!</p>",
            "title": "Michael R."
          }
        },
        "media_6Fq4TE": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/7_162f3256-a6b0-41a7-bb56-55c01b642e94.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/7_162f3256-a6b0-41a7-bb56-55c01b642e94.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>These bikes are the bomb!!!!!! Completely satisfied with our purchase of two Hunter Pro bikes. Easy to assemble, a very short learning curve - and an intuitive app.</p>",
            "title": "Hazer"
          }
        },
        "media_EQqnDg": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/5_cca13ef3-16b4-4122-bcc8-34f8328b75e2.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/5_cca13ef3-16b4-4122-bcc8-34f8328b75e2.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>The retro revolt pro bike is the greatest bike I’ve ever ridden I like it so much I’m thinking about becoming a dealer or buying a couple dozen and reselling them!</p>",
            "title": "Raspy Rides"
          }
        },
        "media_8aA4gV": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/8_c99749df-7588-4579-bb96-237fa925160e.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/8_c99749df-7588-4579-bb96-237fa925160e.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>My new bike was shipped very promptly. Received in excellent condition. Assembly was very easy and intuitive. Riding the Thunder is so much fun. I'm 55 and feel like a kid again. Thank you Jasion!</p>",
            "title": "Scot R.A."
          }
        },
        "media_aDaPiY": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/1_fbd9bec1-285d-418d-bf15-f117161676c3.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/product-image2.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>My husband has enjoyed this e-bike! It’s great for the price point. He likes that it has gears. The seat is very comfortable. The bike came within 2 weeks.</p>",
            "title": "Annette S. "
          }
        },
        "media_aX9Kyq": {
          "type": "media",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/3_5c036d94-8611-471f-980c-652507a75acb.png",
            "mobile_image": "shopify://shop_images/3_5c036d94-8611-471f-980c-652507a75acb.png",
            "score": 5,
            "intro": "<p>This was a gift bought for my husband. He takes it hunting and to pull deer out of the woods. He said it rides very smooth even on rough terrain.</p>",
            "title": "Papa"
          }
        }
      },
